		<title>전망치를 뛰어넘었으나 중국 리스크로 인해 주가는 하락한 엔비디아</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/ko/analysis/market-news/nvidia-beats-expectations-but-shares-drop-on-china</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 06:30:02 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[마켓 뉴스 및 자료]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[stocks]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[최신 소식]]></category>
